kathmandu , nepal -lrb- cnn -rrb- rescue crews and residents in nepal early sunday began the desperate search for survivors after a magnitude-7 .8 quake near the capital of kathmandu a day earlier flattened homes , buildings and temples , causing widespread damage across the region and killing more than 1,800 people .
dozens of bodies were pulled from the historic nine-story dharahara tower that came crashing down during the quake .
at least 17 people were reported killed on mount everest , where the quake caused multiple avalanches .
the death toll of 1,832 is expected to rise as the full extent of the damage is assessed .